title: Primech AI to debut Hytron bathroom cleaning robot at CES 2026
description:
Hytron uses an AI-driven platform to clean all restroom touchpoints while also controlling water application to minimize slip risk. 

The post Primech AI to debut Hytron bathroom cleaning robot at CES 2026 appeared first on The Robot Report.
